tv.amwa.maj.union.impl

Class TimecodeClipImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • tv.amwa.maj.union.impl.TimecodeClipImpl

  • public class TimecodeClipImpl
extends Object

    Implementation of a reference to part of a timecode segment.

    Note that the value of timecode segment calculations in the MAJ API is still being determined. At the current time, this class is only used by non-public methods.

    See Also:
    SourcePackage.specifyValidCodeRange(tv.amwa.maj.model.DataDefinition, int, tv.amwa.maj.record.Rational, long, long)
